text: David Dibben (born 1 December 1958) is a Caymanian former cyclist. He competed in the individual road race and the team time trial events at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:Caymanian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of the Cayman Islands Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
